Nadeau is a competent professor who really knows his stuff. He cares about his students' understanding, even the least important detail. His exams can swing any way, and are very difficult. His PowerPoints have too much information without structure. His lectures are too quick and heavy, and leave you tired at the end. I would not take him again.
Excellent professeur qui transmet sa matière avec passion et humour. Mise en garde : il est nécessaire de lire la jurisprudence avec beaucoup d'attention, car sinon ça vous hantera à l'examen.
Quel excellent prof! Exigeant, mais ça en vaut la peine. Avec son petit côté théâtral, aucun cours n'est plate!
